items.title: Neat Project
items.markdown:
![hi](/Images/hi.jpeg)

Things to support: 
- Read metadata (public to actually display, URL to display URL)
- Converts into cool-looking thing
Sections:
- Home
- Likes
- Blog
Home has location, links for meals, info, projects
Likes just has random things I find cool (date-time stamped)
Blog is just a blog (need metadata tag from Obsidian)
Projects: Table of 3, with image, tags, optional links, and a brief description

Blog: same setup except only 1 horizontally displaced, and optional image to the left (still same setup i.e. links / supported by Obsidian)

# Hi
$$2+2=4$$
